## Health Check Rápido

```python
# Verificar gateway LiteLLM
neocortex_litellm(action="gateway.health")
# → {"gateway_online": true, "models_available": [...]}

# Verificar todas as portas do stack
neocortex_health(action="metrics.live")
# → {"ports": {"4000": "UP", "11434": "UP", "8765": "UP"}}

# Verificar pulse scheduler
neocortex_system(action="pulse.status")
```

